{"TopicId":187838,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Question regarding Kerbal Space Program 2 and 1.","CreatedByName":"A Random Kerbonaut","CreatedById":196468,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-29T21:55:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"A Random Kerbonaut","CreatedById":196468,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-29T21:55:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Kerbal Space Program 2 is released, will the original game still get major updates, or bug fixes? Just general attention to the original because I don\u0027t know if I will buy the second.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-29T22:11:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223663040\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567115735\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196468\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022A Random Kerbonaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, A Random Kerbonaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen Kerbal Space Program 2 is released, will the original game still get major updates, or bug fixes? Just general attention to the original because I don\u0027t know if I will buy the second.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSimplicity","CreatedById":183959,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-30T23:23:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Screenshot2019082207.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022211.11\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 width=\u0022363\u0022 src=\u0022https://u.cubeupload.com/RocketSimplicity/Screenshot2019082207.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Apollo13","CreatedById":74572,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-31T23:45:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I expect to see less mod content as modders rush to the new game in town.\u00A0 I\u0027m not excited about KSP 2.\u00A0 I see it as the death knell for KSP 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-31T23:49:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223664565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567295126\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274572\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Apollo13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Apollo13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I expect to see less mod content as modders rush to the new game in town.\u00A0 I\u0027m not excited about KSP 2.\u00A0 I see it as the death knell for KSP 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have the feeling that mods will still exist in KSP,for none other then the fact that there will always be things that can be done in KSP that cant be done in KSP 2, just as it is true the opposite. Also,not everyone is gonna buy KSP 2, so they\u0027ll have to find their mods somewhere :).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-31T23:49:18Z\u0022 title=\u002208/31/2019 11:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 31, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by nascarlaser1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-01T23:01:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223664565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567295126\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274572\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Apollo13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, Apollo13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not excited about KSP 2.\u00A0 I see it as the death knell for KSP 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know.\u00A0 It\u0027s going to suck when KSP1 gets erased from all the hard drives when KSP2 comes out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T10:07:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567378874\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know.\u00A0 It\u0027s going to suck when KSP1 gets erased from all the hard drives when KSP2 comes out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHah!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a plan!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll keep a copy of my KSP1 on a tape!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T12:00:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567418873\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022107529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Curveball Anders\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Curveball Anders said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHah!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a plan!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll keep a copy of my KSP1 on a tape!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood job, you\u0027ve now forced them to EMP pulse the entire planet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T12:07:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665509\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567425616\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood job, you\u0027ve now forced them to EMP pulse the entire planet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHah, paper tape! 5 hole baudot!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T13:28:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665514\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567426062\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022107529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Curveball Anders\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Curveball Anders said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHah, paper tape! 5 hole baudot!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that is probably 8000 km tape. You know burning it on an dvd would be a bit more practical \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T14:40:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567430901\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022magnemoe\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, magnemoe said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndvd\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo way, dvd can be microwaved. Them planes flying over my house might do it, while spraying their happy-happy joy-joy chems.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI say we chisel the binary bitcode into stone tablets. And draw instructions on reading the code on the walls of the cave we store them in. 100000 years from now, when the survivor descendants of the impending apocalypse seek refuge in this cave, they will spontaneously evolve into the most intelligent species on the planet, simultaneously going extinct because of spending all their time trying to send rocks into orbit instead of foraging for food.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHumanity will end but hey, as endings go, this has got to be a good one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T15:16:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567430901\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022magnemoe\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, magnemoe said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that is probably 8000 km tape. You know burning it on an dvd would be a bit more practical \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe technology to read a DVD is quite advanced.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI prefer punched mylar tape, can in worst case be read by hand \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T18:54:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis discussion of the game\u0027s development has been moved to Development Discussions.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-02T23:29:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis discussion has turned into how to prevent the KSP 2 Boogaloo.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EI\u0027m so proud of this community.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-03T00:12:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaintaining a pure copy of KSP1 in the event of a nuclear winter is of extreme importance.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-03T17:25:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223665856\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567469577\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaintaining a pure copy of KSP1 in the event of a nuclear winter is of extreme importance.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd encasing it in a lead block.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"peteletroll","CreatedById":144573,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-04T18:43:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI suggest backing up KSP1 in cuneiform on clay tablet, because of tested durability.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-09-04T18:44:31Z\u0022 title=\u002209/04/2019 06:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 4, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by peteletroll\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"A Random Kerbonaut","CreatedById":196468,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-25T22:36:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also bury the tablet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T16:14:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many copies of KSP can be written on one DNA molecule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ratwerke_Actual","CreatedById":189744,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T22:37:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223710429\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221574871298\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many copies of KSP can be written on one DNA molecule?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.extremetech.com/extreme/134672-harvard-cracks-dna-storage-crams-700-terabytes-of-data-into-a-single-gram\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.extremetech.com/extreme/134672-harvard-cracks-dna-storage-crams-700-terabytes-of-data-into-a-single-gram\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evandisoft","CreatedById":140442,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-01T12:01:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223664565\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221567295126\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274572\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Apollo13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/31/2019 at 4:45 PM, Apollo13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, I expect to see less mod content as modders rush to the new game in town.\u00A0 I\u0027m not excited about KSP 2.\u00A0 I see it as the death knell for KSP 1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy wish is that Squad is incentivized to create some very cool new features, then the two dev teams start actively competing as if they are rival games, people buy dlc for both games, and we have two competing space simulator games.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-12-01T12:03:19Z\u0022 title=\u002212/01/2019 12:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 1, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by evandisoft\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-01T23:12:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223712048\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575201719\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140442\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022evandisoft\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, evandisoft said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy wish is that Squad is incentivized to create some very cool new features, then the two dev teams start actively competing as if they are rival games, people buy dlc for both games, and we have two competing space simulator games.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really a great business model having an IP compete against itself.\u00A0 Hopefully Simple Rockets 2 can be the proper competition for KSP2.\u00A0 Competition KSP1 never had, which a lack of, I feel, lead to some of the lack luster features such as career mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evandisoft","CreatedById":140442,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-01T23:54:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223712298\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575241961\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really a great business model having an IP compete against itself.\u00A0 Hopefully Simple Rockets 2 can be the proper competition for KSP2.\u00A0 Competition KSP1 never had, which a lack of, I feel, lead to some of the lack luster features such as career mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nYes, it was great initially and then they did nothing with it. They seem to be doing more recently though, and its probably because of KSP2. I\u0027m just wondering if that could work, because possibly their competition would lead to better features and more money. Though I suppose this is just a silly hope born of me owning KSP1 already and not wanting to have to buy\u00A0 another game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}